description:
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;Do you want to work in a growing team where you’ll work to ensure the smooth, coordinated running of Technology Appraisal and Highly Specialised Technology Committee Meetings?&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h1&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;The role:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;Reporting to the Programme Manager, the Assistant Project Manager will be responsible for leading the committee operational functions, managingthe Technology Appraisal Committees as an entity and liaisingbetween the Committee and NICE.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;In order to be successful, you will need to be highly organised with excellent communication and interpersonal skills.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h1&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;What you will bring to the role:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;br /&gt; &lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;The ability to communicate confidently and deal effectively with individuals at all levels both within and outside the organisation, including the ability to formally verbally present complex information to external groups of stakeholders. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;Responsibility for arranging effective project team support &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;Overseeing virtual committee meetings, including managing attendees and providing on the day virtual support as required.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;Identifying areas of established working practice/operational procedure that can be improved, developing the new process, communicating the development (internally and externally) and implementing the changes&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h1&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;The department:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;The Centre for Health Technology Evaluation develops guidance on the use of new and existing medicines, medical devices, diagnostics, treatments and procedures within the NHS.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;The Planning and Operations team provides process oversight, management and support to the Technology Appraisals and Highly Specialised Technology team and the committees that it manages.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;For an informal discussion please contact Mandy Brereton, Assistant Project Manager – mandy.brereton@nice.org.uk&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt; &lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt; Interview date: Monday 7 December 2020.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt; &lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt; &lt;strong&gt;&lt;em&gt;Please note the closing date will be brought forward if we are attracting a large volume of applications. We advise that if you are interested in applying, that you complete and submit your application as soon as possible to avoid disappointment.&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
